  "title": "Associate Business Analyst (AI, AWS, project management)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Requirements / Qualifications:</strong></p><p>1. Has at least 3 - 4 years experience in Data warehousing/AI & Analytics projects.</p><p>2. Has implementation involvement in at least 3 - 4 project cycles</p><p>3. Has at least 1 - 2 years experience in project management</p><p>4. Has at least 3 - 4 years experience in gathering and documenting business requirements from end-users</p><p>5. Preferably with experience in healthcare industry, with broad understanding of healthcare business processes like patient administration, patient medical and non-medical services.</p><p>6. Understanding and hands on experience in all phases of project lifecycle.</p><p>7. Strong communication skills and end-user focused.</p><p>8. Effective written and verbal communication skills.</p><p>9. Team player to ensure team meets delivery targets.</p><p>10. Has technical skills and knowledge on Databases – Databricks, AWS RDS; Visualization – Tableau; ETL software – Informatica; Scripting – SQL or Python</p><p>11. Degree in Computer Science, Computer Engineering or equivalent</p><p>12. Preferably with experience in Informatica IDMC and\\or OBIEE/Tableau.</p>",
