    "description": "<p>We are a team of young professionals with an entrepreneurial mindset come together to redefine the talent that accelerate innovation, growth, and sustainability of the business.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We live in a world of complexity and uncertainty, whether its economy or business. And its technology that drives constant change. A business needs the right people, working collaboratively and effectively and that’s where we come in.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Exa- is a new brand that is locally breaded with an international exposure. We bring in a strong persuasion, collaborating with the expertise and network of professionals across IT.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We value and believe in our team, and we start with understanding a candidate’s ambitions. Aspiring ahead with them by - coaching, guiding, investing in their training, and upskilling throughout their career.</p>",
